        launchSub:
            "In 2020, we expanded our wings internationally with the launch in the US, spreading our honks across borders. Simultaneously, we diversified our offerings, introducing new products at honking speeds to meet the evolving needs of our members.",
        seed: "Seed + funding",
        seedSub:
            "Seeds of potential sprouted in 2021 as we secured additional funding, propelling us to new heights. Always growing, our mission to safeguard what matters most remained steadfast.",
        V3: "Launched App V3",
