        today: "Today",
        membersToday: "150,000+ members",
        membersTodaySub:
            "As of today, our flock has grown to include over 150,000 members. The skies are vast, and we continue to soar, dedicated to safeguarding the futures of our members with unwavering commitment and innovative solutions.",
        flockGrowing: "Our flock is growing!",
        growingSub:
            "Keeping the world insured is tough work, but someone has to do it. Maybe you? We’re looking for talented people to join us in our mission of making insurance accessible and affordable.",
        goToCareers: "Go To Careers →",
