        today: "Today",
        membersToday: "150,000+ members",
        membersTodaySub:
            "As of today, our herd has grown to include over 150,000 members. The skies are vast, and we continue to soar, dedicated to safeguarding the futures of our members with unwavering commitment and innovative solutions.",
        flockGrowing: "Our herd is growing!",
        growingSub:
            "Keeping the world insured is tough work, but someone has to do it. Maybe you? We’re looking for talented people to join us in our mission of making insurance accessible and affordable.",
        goToCareers: "Go To Careers →",
    },
    [frCA]: {
        tabTitle: "À propos",
        mainStatement: "Assurer le monde, une police à la fois.",
        subStatement:
            "L'assurance peut être compliquée... mais cela ne doit pas l'être. Goose élimine les aspects complexes de l'achat d'assurance et facilite plus que jamais l'obtention de la couverture adéquate. Et tout cela se fait en quelques secondes, depuis une seule application.",
        gooseInNumber: "Goose en chiffres",
        numMembers: "150,000+",
        gooseMembers: "Membres de Goose",
        gooseMembersSub:
